nodes.text: A blue nebula was located in the Kwymar sector of the Outer Rim Territories. It could be seen from the portion of space around the planet of Telos IV. When Meetra Surik, her apprentice Visas Marr, and Mandalore the Preserver secretly boarded the starship Ravager in 3951 BBY, they caught a glimpse of the blue nebula through a large hole in the hull.
